<refsect2 id="gtk-volume-button-new" role="function" condition="since:2.12">
<title>gtk_volume_button_new ()</title>
<indexterm zone="gtk-volume-button-new" role="2.12"><primary sortas="volume_button_new">gtk_volume_button_new</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="GtkWidget">GtkWidget</link>*          gtk_volume_button_new               (void);</programlisting>
<para>
Creates a <link linkend="GtkVolumeButton"><type>GtkVolumeButton</type></link>, with a range between 0.0 and 1.0, with
a stepping of 0.02. Volume values can be obtained and modified using
the functions from <link linkend="GtkScaleButton"><type>GtkScaleButton</type></link>.</para>
